    <abstract id="aspace_8a3c1aad37b906785013fcd825e925b8">The German Nationality Room Committee Collection details the planning, funding, and construction of the German Nationality Room in the Cathedral of Learning. The dates of the documents range from 1927 to 1954, and are in both English and German. The collection contains correspondence, finical statements, newspaper clippings, booklets, minutes, programs, a running memo, photographs and other materials related to the German Nationality Room.</abstract>
